<body>
<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>OPD Pediatric Case Sheet</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen will capture Pediatric patient case sheet details.
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/opd_Paediatrics.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<img src="images/opd_PaediatricsPlan.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>
 <span class="title">Service Personnel Details:</span> 
    <br />Based on selection of patient all service personal details will come from MI Room.
<br />
    <span class="title">Patient Details:</span> 
    <br />Based on selection of patient all patient details will come from MI Room.
<br />
    <span class="title">Vaccine Plan:</span> 
    <br />User can view the existing vaccine details and user want to give another dose user can press <b>Vaccination Button.</b>
<br />
    <span class="title">Vaccination (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on Vaccination button user can create vaccination plan for patient.
    <br />Each patient first visit user can plan like Vaccine, no of days, vaccine date, completion date and remarks.

<br />
    <span class="title">Date of Birth:</span> 
    <br />Based on selection of patient date of birth details will come from registration screen.
<br />
    <span class="title">Referred By:</span> 
    <br />User can select the referred doctors from the given list, it will shows only doctors.

<br />
    <span class="title">Wt:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient weight.
<br />
    <span class="title">Ht:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient height.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Hc:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient Hc.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">OFC:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient OFC.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">RR:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient RR.

    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Clinical Notes:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient clinical details and observations.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Exp.HT:</span> 
    <br />User can write Father Height in CM , Mother Height in CM and Childâ€™s Age  then press calculate Button
    <br />Then CHILD Height in CM, 3rd Percentile and 97th Percentile will calculate automatically.

    <br />
    <span class="title">Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient disease observation details.
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">BMI Categories:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient Height in centimeters.
    <br />User can write patient weight in kilograms.
    <br />Then press Compute Button then it will calculate patient BMI.
    <br />Ex:
    <br />Normal weight = 18.5-24.9 
    <br />Overweight = 25-29.9
    <br />Obesity = BMI of 30 or greater


 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on submit button user can save the data. 
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">View (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on view button user can view the previous visit details.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Reset (Button):</span> 
    <br />Clicking on reset button, will clear the current or existing data.
   
</p>
</div>
